Bounds

A rectangle in geographical coordinates from points at the southwest and northeast corners.

Field Required Type Description

northeast

optional LatLngLiteral See LatLngLiteral for more information.

southwest

optional LatLngLiteral See LatLngLiteral for more information.

Example 

{
  "northeast": {
    "lat": 49.315678,
    "lng": 4.15292
  },
  "southwest": {
    "lat": 49.31073,
    "lng": 4.145162
  }
}
